{"lemma":"عِدَة","slug":"عِدَة","root":"#.ع.د","root_slug":"_-ع-د","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ع-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عِدَة","root":"عدد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28274","n28285","n28286","n42115"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%90%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"appliance, fixture, technical provision","examples":[{"text":"وممّا شاع من أفعال مولانا أيده الله في الجهاد إنشاؤه الأجفان بجميع السواحل واستكثاره من عُدَد البحر وهذا في زمان الصلح والمُهادنة إعْدادًا لأيّام القِرة وأخذًا بالحزم في قطع أَطْماع الكفّار.","english":"One of the most notable deeds of our master (God assist him!) of struggle is his engineering of enceintes on all shores, and his manifold provisions in naval matters, in time of peace and armistice to prepare for days of war, to shortcircuit the cravings of the infidels resolutely."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"raw material, ground-stuff, commodity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"number","examples":[{"text":"هذا باب تثنية ما كان منقوصاً وكان عدة حروفه أربعة أحرف فزائدًا"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"several, a number of","examples":[{"text":"سَأَلْتُهَا عِدَّةَ مَرَاتٍ","english":"I asked her several times"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a waiting period upon a woman after her marriage has ended"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَعَدَ (waʕada) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʕud.da/","/ʕid.da/","/ʕi.da/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28274","headword_ar":"عَدَّهُ","root":"Ed","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, O, Msb, &c.,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~N","text_ar":"عَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~apN","text_ar":"عِدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEodaAdN","text_ar":"تَعْدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[which last has an intensive signification, and may also be regarded as an inf. n. of the verb next following]; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ed~dhu","text_ar":"عدّدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or this latter has an intensive signification; (Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He numbered, counted, reckoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"computed, it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, O, Msb, K:) [and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiEotad~ahu","text_ar":"اِعْتَدَّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"sometimes signifies the same, as is shown by what here follows:]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"famaA lakumo Ealayohin~a mino Eid~apK taEotad~uwnahaA","text_ar":"فَمَا لَكُمْ عَلَيْهِنَّ مِنْ عِدَّةٍ تَعْتَدُّونَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur xxxiii. 48, means ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Then there shall not be for you, as incumbent on them, any"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~ap","text_ar":"عِدَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"(q. v.)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which ye shall count the number"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of the days]: (Bd, Jel:) or the meaning is,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of which ye shall exact the accomplishment of the number"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of the days]: (Ksh, Bd:) and Lh has mentioned, as heard from the Arabs,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadadotu Ald~araAhima A^aforaAdFA","text_ar":"عَدَدْتُ الدَّرَاهِمَ اَفْرَادًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wiHaAdFA","text_ar":"وِحَادًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I counted the dirhems by single pieces"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEodadotu","text_ar":"اَعْدَدْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, followed by the same words; then adding, “ I know not whether it [i. e. the latter] be from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEadadu","text_ar":"العَدَدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEud~apu","text_ar":"العُدَّةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"” [i. e. whether the meaning be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I counted"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I prepared"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"provided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"the latter of which is a well-known meaning]: his doubt indicates that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEodadotu","text_ar":"اَعْدَدْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadadotu","text_ar":"عَدَدْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but [SM says] “ I know it not.” (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~a","text_ar":"عَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is doubly trans.: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadadotuka AlmaAla","text_ar":"عَدَدْتُكَ المَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as well as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eadadotu laka AlmaAla","text_ar":"عَدَدْتُ لَكَ المَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[both meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I numbered, counted, reckoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"computed, to thee the articles of property"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eud~a fiY qawomK","text_ar":"عُدَّ فِى قَوْمٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was numbered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckoned, among a people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"party."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) [And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~a maHaAsinahu","text_ar":"عَدَّ مَحَاسِنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~adahaA","text_ar":"عَدَّدَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~N","text_ar":"عَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and of either"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEodaAdN","text_ar":"تَعْدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He enumerated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"recounted, his good qualities"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"actions:"},{"kind":"text","text":"a phrase of frequent occurrence.] ―         -b2-  [Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He counted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he accounted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"esteemed, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"good or bad &c.:] one says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~ahu HasanFA","text_ar":"عَدَّهُ حَسَنًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He counted, accounted, reckoned,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"esteemed, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"goodly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisotaHosanahu","text_ar":"اِسْتَحْسَنَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hsn","text_ar":"حسن"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEtd~","text_ar":"اعتدّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ead~a","text_ar":"عَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in this sense]; whence the saying,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wayaEotad~uhu qawomN kaviyrN tijaArapF"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And many people count it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reckon it, as merchandise"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Har p. 127.)"}],"source_refs":["O","Msb","S","K","A","Bd","Jel","Ksh"]},{"entry_id":"n28285","headword_ar":"عُدَّةٌ","root":"Ed","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Apparatus, equipments"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equipage, accoutrements, furniture, gear, tackle"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tackling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, L, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that one has prepared for the casualties of fortune,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"consisting of property and weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of implements, instruments, tools,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like, and of beasts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) accord. to some, formed from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EutodapN","text_ar":"عُتْدَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]; but others deny this: (L in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Etd","text_ar":"عتد"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EudadN","text_ar":"عُدَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a liloA^amori Eud~atahu","text_ar":"اَخَذَ لِلْاَمْرِ عُدَّتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EataAdahu","text_ar":"عَتَادَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took, for the affair, his apparatus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he prepared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"provided, himself for the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: both signify the same. (S, O.) ―         -b2-  Also, (S, O,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~N","text_ar":"عِدٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", this latter of the dial. of Temeem, (A'Obeyd, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A state of preparation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A'Obeyd, S, O, Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuwnuwA EalaY Eud~apK","text_ar":"كُونُوا عَلَى عُدَّةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be ye in a state of preparation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eud~N","text_ar":"عُدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","L","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n28286","headword_ar":"عِدَّةٌ","root":"Ed","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"an inf. n. of 1[q. v.]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A number collected together; a number collectively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^ayotu Eid~apa rijaAlK","text_ar":"رَاَيْتُ عِدَّةَ رِجَالٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I saw a number of men collected together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anofa*otu Eid~apa","text_ar":"اَنْفَذْتُ عِدَّةَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kutubK","text_ar":"كُتُبٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I transmitted a number of letters together."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~apu AlmaroA^api","text_ar":"عِدَّةُ المَرْاَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The days of the menstruation of the woman,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which she numbers, when she has been divorced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when her husband has died;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until the expiration of which she may not marry again;"},{"kind":"text","text":"the period being, in the case of a divorced woman, not pregnant, that of three menstruations]; or [in the case of a pregnant woman]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the days of her pregnancy;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or [in the case of a widow not pregnant]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"four months and ten nights:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the woman's waiting the prescribed time after divorce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after the death of her husband, until she may marry again:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the days of the woman's mourning for a husband, and of abstaining from the wearing of ornaments &c.;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) whether it be a period of months or of menstruations, or the period completed by her giving birth to offspring in her womb, which she has conceived by her husband: (TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EidadN","text_ar":"عِدَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoqaDato Eid~atuhaA","text_ar":"اِنْقَضَتْ عِدَّتُهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eid~ap","text_ar":"عِدَّة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,) from the period of the death of her husband, or of his divorcing her. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinoqaDato Eid~apu Alr~ajuli","text_ar":"اِنْقَضَتْ عِدَّةُ الرَّجُلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The man's term of life ended:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EidadN","text_ar":"عِدَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-  And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN A_in~amaA yaA^otiY A^aholahu","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ اـِنَّمَا يَاْتِى اَهْلَهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEid~apa","text_ar":"العِدَّةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one comes to his wife,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"family, only once in the month,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the two months."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, L.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EidaAdN","text_ar":"عِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places."}],"source_refs":["S","O","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n42115","headword_ar":"عِدَةٌ","root":"wEd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waEodN","text_ar":"وَعْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and 1."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}